orial Sloan Kettering Brooklyn Infusion Center</a>.\r\n\r\nLife Essentials, a welcoming kit:\r\nThe kit presented to Memorial Sloan Kettering was created to allow new chemo patients to feel more at home, relaxed, and like honored guests.\r\n\r\n<em>The kit includes: A personalized hand written welcome letter, herbal tea samples, aroma therapy oil samples, a healthy snack, an eye mask, a journal with mood and weather note sections. In addition the most important part is My Preferences which is a checklist and service that allows the patient to customize their visits - everything from favorite music, to the type of tea they would like and at what part of the day. This is a bespoke welcome service with every day essentials to make the chemo therapy experience as stress free as possible. </em>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/cargocollective-5.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-62 aligncenter\" title=\"cargocollective-5\" src=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/cargocollective-5-891x1024.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"713\" height=\"819\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img title=\"gallery\" src=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-includes/js/tinymce/plugins/wpgallery/img/t.gif\" alt=\"\" />[portfolio_slideshow exclude=\"79\" slideheight=400]\r\n\r\n<img title=\"gallery\" src=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-includes/js/tinymce/plugins/wpgallery/img/t.gif\" alt=\"\" />','Life Essentials, a welcoming kit.','','publish','open','open','','this-is-another-project','','','2012-05-25 16:45:36','2012-05-25 20:45:36','',0,'http://localhost:8080/?post_type=project&#038;p=53',0,'project','',0),(226,1,'2012-05-16 03:01:51','2012-05-16 03:01:51','','icons-02','','inherit','open','open','','icons-02','','','2012-05-16 03:01:51','2012-05-16 03:01:51','',8,'http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/icons-02.