as just on an MTV Panel contracted by WHATIF.\r\n\r\nI grew up in the country side. My passport is almost full. I\'m a pro at Where\'s Waldo, a puzzle master, and an \'Eye Spy\' guru. Design is serious play for me, a puzzle, and always a challenge. I\'d rather listen to music than watch TV. I like sending mail. I appreciate tactile feedback. I get competitive on the foose-ball table - and like a good challenge. Right now I\'m probably working on a project. Find me on twitter and we inspire each other.\r\n<div style=\"float: right; width: 35%; clear: right;\">\r\n\r\n[skills][skill value=\"100\" color=\"red\" text=\"Tennis\"][skill value=\"80\" color=\"yellow\" text=\"Hockey\"]\r\n\r\n[skill value=\"90\" color=\"blue\" text=\"Eating Ice cream\"]\r\n\r\n[skill value=\"65\" color=\"gray\" text=\"Eating Candy\"]\r\n\r\n[skill value=\"45\" color=\"green\" text=\"Yelling\"]\r\n\r\n[skill value=\"35\" color=\"brown\" text=\"Sleeping\"]\r\n\r\n[/skills]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[twitter username=micahspear]','About','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-38','','','2012-05-13 04:11:26','2012-05-13 04:11:26','',4,'http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=198',0,'revision','',0),(197,1,'2012-05-13 04:10:43','2012-05-13 04:10:43','<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-75\" style=\"margin-bottom: 50px;\" title=\"Micah Spear Portrait\" src=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/hoeweler_micah_final2-214x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"214\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<div style=\"float: right; width: 35%; clear: right;\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhy:\r\n\r\nI\'m constantly inspired and motivated to invent and develop valuable ideas. Some of the most remarkable inventions were created by accident. That alone pushes me to experiment and be open to the unknown. I\'m interested in producing disruptive products. With the bottom line in mind, I intend on bringing design and technology closer - thoughtfully - and with consideration for our needs